{"tid":731652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李克強：中國永遠不會發動貿易戰","createTime":"2018-07-06T11:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T23:57:23.000Z","uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f62ef1774085789485450f2a07344caf9b6703f3","tid":731652,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:15:12.000Z","msg":"美國在今日本港時間中午12時，對總值340億美元中國商品加徵關稅。正進行訪問歐洲的中國國務院總理李克強表示，貿易戰絕不會是解決貿易爭端的方法。<br />\n<br />\n李克強在記者會中稱，中國永不會開始貿易戰，惟會採取措施。他批評，貿易戰對任何人都無好處，無人在戰爭中成為勝利者，又指貿易戰只會傷害挑起事端者。<br />\n<br />\n李克強昨日抵保加利亞首都索非亞，出席第7次中國與中東歐國家領導人會晤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.oushinet.com/u/cms/www/image/20171127/20171127214117_965.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.oushinet.com%2Fu%2Fcms%2Fwww%2Fimage%2F20171127%2F20171127214117_965.jpg&h=440cf69b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource (明報) : <a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1530871542150&amp;issue=20180706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1530871542150%26issue%3D20180706&d=0eyK77BLoCEK96fm%2BgHxWDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=48dcb82d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1530871542150&amp;issue=20180706</a>"},{"pid":"dd0df77fd17d4c293369adbf85b8e439e1508fbc","tid":731652,"uid":35382,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"若然屬實"},{"pid":"3c7df7871d8ea782692e8901d1a1066bac63e2c4","tid":731652,"uid":30067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"又話亮劍"},{"pid":"3c5f7318314b2b4b4f1231c494b2c6b46834ae3d","tid":731652,"uid":56546,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"之前話全面反擊, 中國成最後贏家<br />\n依家又嚇到瀨曬屎話兩個都係輸家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634e0454a4faae60af208c5f6